---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Morrisontech"
  description="Learn how Morrisontech builds better websites using cutting-edge AI development tools."
>
  <div class="bg-brand-dark pt-32 pb-16 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About Morrisontech</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Australian IT, built for the way business works today.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 space-y-12">

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Who we are</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Morrisontech is an Australian IT business specialising in professional website
        design and development. We work with small and medium businesses across Australia
        to build fast, modern websites that make a strong first impression and turn
        visitors into customers.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        We're owner-operated — when you work with Morrisontech, you deal directly with
        the person building your site. No account managers, no handoffs, no surprises.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">What makes us different</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We use the latest AI development tools — including Claude Code by Anthropic —
        throughout our build process. This isn't a gimmick. It means we can deliver
        a professionally built website in significantly less time than a traditional
        agency, at a lower cost, without cutting corners on quality.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        Every line of code is reviewed by a human developer. The AI accelerates the
        work; the expertise ensures it's done right.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">The technology</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We build with modern frameworks — Astro for fast static business sites,
        Next.js for applications that need more — styled with Tailwind CSS and
        deployed in Docker containers on Linux servers. It's a lean, reliable stack
        that loads fast and is straightforward to maintain.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="bg-brand-accent hover:opacity-90 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md transition-opacity inline-block"
      >
        Let's talk about your project
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
